  (text "KEY MATRIX  5x12 (59 keys, COL2ROW diodes)" (exclude_from_sim no) (at 25.4 20.32 0) (effects (font (size 3.81 3.81) (thickness 0.3) bold) (justify left bottom)) (uuid "9f25e9b2-d2ce-5800-a946-07c4936512bc"))
  (text "MCU -- RP2040 (VERIFY pin numbers before fab, see file header)" (exclude_from_sim no) (at 96.52 100.33 0) (effects (font (size 3.81 3.81) (thickness 0.3) bold) (justify left bottom)) (uuid "e877940c-c973-557f-b2f3-be7a0e73a1d0"))
  (text "RP2040 minimum system (core regulator, 12MHz xtal, QSPI flash)" (exclude_from_sim no) (at 96.52 63.5 0) (effects (font (size 3.0 3.0) (thickness 0.3) bold) (justify left bottom)) (uuid "087ee821-851d-5b20-a9a6-c5e596f3c972"))
  (text "Wireless (CYW43439, BLE-only) -- crystal/pinout/power topology verified against datasheet 002-30348 Rev *D; RF matching values still VERIFY (vendor/antenna-specific)" (exclude_from_sim no) (at 96.52 114.3 0) (effects (font (size 2.5 2.5) (thickness 0.3) bold) (justify left bottom)) (uuid "782d479c-96e1-5b1f-b64a-66f35d842afa"))
  (text "Per-key RGB -- SK6812MINI-E x59, serpentine chain (must match Sources/smk/RGBLighting.swift ledChainIndex)" (exclude_from_sim no) (at 25.4 45.72 0) (effects (font (size 3.0 3.0) (thickness 0.3) bold) (justify left bottom)) (uuid "296df22c-728e-581d-870d-4530409f35ee"))
  (text "RGB power budget (calculated from the SK6812MINI-E datasheet, 12mA/channel x 3 x 59 LEDs = 2.12A max at full white): fed from VSYS, NOT the 3.3V LDO (AP2112K-3.3 isn't remotely rated for this). D60 (B5819W, ~1A avg rating) IS in this path when USB-powered and WOULD be exceeded by 2.12A -- firmware must cap brightness/concurrent-on count well below full-white-all-keys regardless of power source. Also VERIFY: SK6812MINI-E's own datasheet specs VDD 3.7-5.5V, and VSYS (Li-ion battery) can sag below 3.7V well within normal discharge range -- LEDs may misbehave on a low battery even with brightness capped. Level shifter keeps DIN threshold margin safe across the VSYS voltage range (separate from the VDD-minimum concern above)." (exclude_from_sim no) (at 25.4 38.1 0) (effects (font (size 1.6 1.6) (thickness 0.3) bold) (justify left bottom)) (uuid "7d669219-ac3e-535c-8975-7713a902e4a4"))
  (text "USB-C  (charge + native USB)" (exclude_from_sim no) (at 219.71 105.41 0) (effects (font (size 3.81 3.81) (thickness 0.3) bold) (justify left bottom)) (uuid "1fdb5884-b899-5512-ad97-84b07a318ae9"))
  (text "Li-ion charger 500mA" (exclude_from_sim no) (at 287.02 105.41 0) (effects (font (size 3.81 3.81) (thickness 0.3) bold) (justify left bottom)) (uuid "3c8b148f-42ad-5108-838d-8a76742d4459"))
  (text "Power path + 3.3V LDO + ON/OFF" (exclude_from_sim no) (at 340.36 105.41 0) (effects (font (size 3.81 3.81) (thickness 0.3) bold) (justify left bottom)) (uuid "aac6a9c6-2175-5405-9ef5-ce206a493eac"))
  (text "VBAT sense + RESET + BOOTSEL" (exclude_from_sim no) (at 391.16 105.41 0) (effects (font (size 3.81 3.81) (thickness 0.3) bold) (justify left bottom)) (uuid "5b7de92f-05ff-5f57-bae9-a445d8c27caa"))
  (text "GPIO map (VERIFY pin numbers, see file header):  ROW0-4 = GPIO0-4   COL0-11 = GPIO5-16   RGB_GPIO = GPIO17   VBAT_SENSE = GPIO26/ADC0   BT UART/ctrl (GPIO18-23, 28) = CYW43439 BLE link (see wireless section)" (exclude_from_sim no) (at 25.4 95.25 0) (effects (font (size 2.0 2.0) (thickness 0.3) bold) (justify left bottom)) (uuid "8333d8b6-055f-5088-a577-349a93816d3e"))
  (text "Charging works with power switch OFF (charger connects before switch).  BOOTSEL+RESET = USB mass-storage bootloader mode (VERIFY)." (exclude_from_sim no) (at 25.4 100.33 0) (effects (font (size 2.0 2.0) (thickness 0.3) bold) (justify left bottom)) (uuid "f69a50b2-69c6-5803-9c77-572fbbd44b12"))
